CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Synergy CHC Corp. is a provider of consumer health care, beauty, and lifestyle products. Synergy's current brand portfolio consists of two marquee brands, FOCUSfactor, a clinically-tested brain health supplement that has been shown to improve memory, concentration and focus, and Flat Tummy, a lifestyle and wellness brand that provides a suite of nutritional products to help women achieve their weight management goals.
